{"tid":541967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭證實被DQ 香港眾志譴責：剝奪組織參選權","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T14:40:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"765540daf5493ec80ea2d640e035ce17927145fb","tid":541967,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517026720_ee54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517026720_ee54.jpg&h=77974dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港眾志中午證實，已報名參加港島區立法會補選的成員告周庭今日收到選舉主任通知，指因其政治聯繫而決定她的提名無效。香港眾志強烈譴責有關決定，指選管會在周庭遞交提名表格後不斷刁難她的國籍問題，但未無就她或眾志的政治立場提出任何查詢和質疑，批評選舉主任今次並無引述周庭過去有何違規的個人言論，單憑香港眾志的政綱就否決周庭，「這等同於剝奪整個組織參選權，禁止所有香港眾志成員踏足議會。」<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志的聲明指出，2016年立法會選舉中，選舉主任曾要求參選人提交補選資料，以確認部份候選人的政見是否符合選舉規定，但今次選舉主任並無要求周庭提交有關資料，認為是將選舉主任的權力放大，「形同賦予選舉主任權力，在決定候選人是否獲有效提名時，判斷其政治立場，甚至不給予參選人辯解的機會」，認為選舉主任是作出一個政治決定，而非跟進既有程序以及政治中立原則。<br />\n聲明重申，即使跟據人大早前的釋法，亦只是限制了宣誓時的形式以及內容，與參選權無關，質疑選舉主任有何權力解釋釋法內容，認為這不單是褫奪候選人資格，更是剝奪市民基本政治權利，形容今次是「中共對一代人的清算」，「政府的動機是要殺盡後雨傘一整代有志從政改變香港、推動民主的年輕人的希望。雨傘運動後的進步力量將會在議會絕跡。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180127/57759833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57759833&d=nNyybF8Xdylwz8xFDQIOosmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=60c1b637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180127%2F57759833&h=079439c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180127/57759833</a>"},{"pid":"3eda423e696938d77fbe18125a363c532d5c7055","tid":541967,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.azquotes.com/picture-quotes/quote-first-they-came-for-the-jews-but-i-did-nothing-because-i-m-not-a-jew-then-they-came-martin-niemoller-54-47-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.azquotes.com%2Fpicture-quotes%2Fquote-first-they-came-for-the-jews-but-i-did-nothing-because-i-m-not-a-jew-then-they-came-martin-niemoller-54-47-15.jpg&h=c89c7df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1fd397f5ee78023f5ec2856a2408dff22845695","tid":541967,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/123914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F123914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=29ad8ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcec565173be116353dde7f5342a1acd01a5f17","tid":541967,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"集會啦 有5000人當贏 跟住繼續推plan b好快無左件事"},{"pid":"e320c7d70734188e75ff4936fa4a40969b6063d6","tid":541967,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"唇亡齒寒<br />\n梁天琦玩完就到中箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5577073dd5104d7a0a9a1373228a1126b73664","tid":541967,"uid":127202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人係咪繼續當無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e4109b02a1cd3f748471ca84e6596bf089d4d7","tid":541967,"uid"